==English==
===Adverbial phrase===
'''[[arse]] [[over]] [[tit]]'''
# {{idiom}} {{vulgar}} [[tumbling|Tumbling]]; [[falling]]; upside-down; unstable or unbalanced.
#:''I missed the step and went '''arse over tit'''.''

